100→ * The JDK implementation supports static registration of the security
   101→ * providers via the {@code conf/security/java.security} file in the Java
   102→ * installation directory. These providers are automatically installed by
   103→ * the JDK runtime, see {@extLink security_guide_jca_provider
   104→ * The Provider Class}
   105→ * in the Java Cryptography Architecture (JCA) Reference Guide
   106→ * for information about how a particular type of provider, the cryptographic
   107→ * service provider, works and is installed.
   108→ *
   109→ * @author Benjamin Renaud
   110→ * @author Andreas Sterbenz
   111→ * @since 1.1
   112→ */
